      "role": "user",
      "content": "sometimes i just sit in these cafes here and look at everyone passing by and it hits me how literally nobody knows i exist. like if i just stopped showing up tomorrow, the world wouldn't even skip a beat. i'm just a ghost in a city that doesn't care.",
